{"tid":430655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揸刀強迫途人飲可樂 警天眼追查拘紮髻男","createTime":"2017-10-10T04:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T04:17:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"638070237013b7469a3ecbcdc5b45a9bf78c4e7f","tid":430655,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171010/large/1507594341_325c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171010%2Flarge%2F1507594341_325c.jpg&h=67a52779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名紮髻男子上周五(6日)在旺角鬧市廣東道近鴉蘭街，失常指罵途人，更持刀強迫老街坊喝下其手上可樂，最後棄刀逃去，警方經過多日追緝，昨晚將他拘捕，疑犯涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子姓李44歲，約6呎高，有黑幫新義安背景，染有不良嗜好，曾涉及傷人及自稱黑社會成員案件，因恐遭人尋仇，故身上經常藏有一把利刀自保，案發當日紮髻男疑吸食毒品後神志錯亂，拔刀強迫途人喝可樂。<br />\n<br />\n旺角反黑組接手追查，連日翻查大批閉路電視記錄，鎖定目標男子。警員昨日接獲線報，於晚上約10時半，掩至旺角砵蘭街一間賓館，將該名男子拘捕，帶返警署調查。今日凌晨2時許，警員帶同疑犯，返回其黃大仙下邨龍智樓居所搜查，但未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57312021&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57312021%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171010&d=VL92U77%2BVVEkm1aF96RxY%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=ccdfdfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57312021%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171010&h=0c724532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57312021&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171010</a>"},{"pid":"75bcc4cae49412c41a8ee77f52ca54dc6b43385f","tid":430655,"uid":138390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg